categories: Category:Battles of the uprising against the First Order

nodes.text: In 35 ABY, in the aftermath of the Battle of Exegol and the death of Darth Sidious, an uprising against the First Order took place on the forest moon of Endor, as the destruction of Sidious' forces at the hands of the Resistance had inspired the inhabitants of the galaxy to rise up. During the uprising, a Resurgent-class Star Destroyer was destroyed via the "Holdo maneuver", which was witnessed by Wicket W. Warrick and Pommet Warrick from Endor's forests. On the night that followed the event, there was feasting and fireworks at the Bright Tree Village.
